<title key="Suckling pig stuffed with suckling pig's lung">Ein <ingredient en="suckling pig" commodity="Q23015">spenvearl</ingredient></title> 
<instruction>NIm ein <ingredient en="suckling pig" commodity="Q23015">spenfearhl</ingredient></instruction> vnd 
<instruction>prat es chuel</instruction> 
<instruction>das spalt enczway mit dem haupp</instruction> so 
<instruction>nym die <ingredient commodity="Q107304893" en="suckling pig lung">lungel</ingredient> vnd iij herte <ingredient en="chicken egg" commodity="Q15260613">ayr</ingredient> vnd ij waiche vnd schoen <ingredient en="bread" commodity="Q7802">prat</ingredient> <ingredient en="saffron" commodity="Q25434">saffran</ingredient> <ingredient en="pepper" commodity="Q3143131">pheffer</ingredient> <ingredient en="table salt" commodity="Q11254">salcz</ingredient></instruction> 
<instruction>hakch das klain</instruction> vnd 
<instruction>tue gehakchten <ingredient en="bacon" commodity="Q11106">spekch</ingredient> darczue</instruction> vnd 
<instruction>vuell das <ingredient en="suckling pig" commodity="Q23015">ferhel</ingredient></instruction> 
<instruction>stekch es an den <tool en="spit" commodity="Q20181361">spis</tool></instruction> 
<instruction>prat es sanft</instruction> 
<instruction>betreuff es mit <ingredient en="lard" commodity="Q72827">smalcz</ingredient></instruction></div></body></text></TEI>